-Your right shoulder.

31:54.033 --> 31:55.667
How many times did you feel it?

31:56.033 --> 31:57.633
-Twice.
-You felt it twice?

31:57.700 --> 31:58.800
Yeah.

31:58.867 --> 32:00.200
Melanie, I didn't touch or come near you.

32:00.267 --> 32:01.967
I actually touched Bill twice
on your right shoulder.

32:02.033 --> 32:04.600
-Isn't that right, Bill?
-Yes, you did.

32:12.500 --> 32:13.800
